## ### You can acquire technics and knowledge for pleasant Mountaineering. ## (GCN) ### Our club also welcomes foreign citizenship who lives in Kansai region for climing with us. Techinics and experiences are not necessary to admit our club. The most important thing is motivation to aim high. Will you step forward to aim high with us. Motivated Beginner is also welcomed. If you are interested in alpine style but having worry about it, you can also move to climing division from traverse division after learning mountainneering basic skils. You will acquire safety mountaineering thoroughly. It is also possible to join training and meeting for tiral. Please feel free to contact us by email We will train beginner of climing from beginning. ## Entry condition. - - - () - Healthy person who is interested in climing. - Experience does not metter. We will train from beginning. - Above 18 years old to up to 55 years old. (Please ask us if you are above 55 years old) ## Membership fee | | | | |---|---|:---| |
Addmission fee||8,000 |
Annual fee|
for General|6,000 | |
for Student|4,000 | |()
for married couple|10,000 | |
for Inactive member|2,000 Mountain insurance is required in each case. ### Personal Information Our club never disclose nor supply personal informartion in email to a third party. ** ** ** Aboout out club, addmission, and trial traing, please feel free to email us !!**

You can acquire technics and knowledge for pleasant Mountaineering.

(GCN)

Our club also welcomes foreign citizenship who lives in Kansai region for climing with us.





Techinics and experiences are not necessary to admit our club.
The most important thing is motivation to aim high.
Will you step forward to aim high with us.
Motivated Beginner is also welcomed.




If you are interested in alpine style but having worry about it,
you can also move to climing division from traverse division after learning mountainneering basic skils.
You will acquire safety mountaineering thoroughly.


It is also possible to join training and meeting for tiral.


Please feel free to contact us by email


We will train beginner of climing from beginning.

Entry condition.

  • ()
  • Healthy person who is interested in climing.
  • Experience does not metter. We will train from beginning.
  • Above 18 years old to up to 55 years old. (Please ask us if you are above 55 years old)

Membership fee

Addmission fee		 8,000

Annual fee
for General		 6,000

for Student		 4,000
()
for married couple		 10,000

for Inactive member		 2,000


Mountain insurance is required in each case.

Personal Information


Our club never disclose nor supply personal informartion in email to a third party.


Aboout out club, addmission, and trial traing, please feel free to email us !!

## 2014 ### We have been challenging rock ridges and walls since our founding in 2014 using alpine style with our ambition.
*** *** *** *** *** *** *** Safety first and thorough basics. *** *** Enforcing self rescue to help our members by ourself. *** *** Founder, former rescue team in Nagano ***
## Organization 1. Climing division. 2. Traverse division. 2251510 Limit of members is total 25(15 for Climing, 10 for Traverse), in order to activate activities. ## Activities - Traning on mountains in Kansai region every mounth. - Having monthly meeting at the office, reporting activities and planning. - 11 Having activities mostly on Japan Alps once a month or every two months. - Having Traning and Activities not only on weekends but also on weekdays. Please email us for further details. ## Members age distribution (2018/6/29 23) | | (Male) | (Female)| |----------------|---------------| | 20 | 3 | | | 30 | 3 | 1 | | 40 | 4 | 1 | | 50 | 2 | 5 | | 60 | 3 | 1 | ## Chairperson () Yoshichika Yamada Professional Alpine Guide for variation route in domestic and overseas.

2014

We have been challenging rock ridges and walls since our founding in 2014 using alpine style with our ambition.





Safety first and thorough basics.
Enforcing self rescue to help our members by ourself.
Founder, former rescue team in Nagano

Organization

  1. Climing division.
  2. Traverse division.
    2251510

    Limit of members is total 25(15 for Climing, 10 for Traverse), in order to activate activities.

Activities


  • Traning on mountains in Kansai region every mounth.

  • Having monthly meeting at the office, reporting activities and planning.
  • 11
    Having activities mostly on Japan Alps once a month or every two months.

  • Having Traning and Activities not only on weekends but also on weekdays.

    Please email us for further details.
